<figure class="viz" aria-labelledby="cm-title">
  <figcaption id="cm-title">
    Compression changes different parts of the deployment contract
  </figcaption>
  <div class="matrix">
    <b>Method</b><b>Changes graph</b><b>Needs retraining</b><b>Runtime requirement</b>
    <strong>Unstructured pruning</strong><span>mask or sparse weights</span><span
      >usually recovery tuning</span
    ><span>sparse kernel support</span>
    <strong>Structured pruning</strong><span>removes heads, channels, layers</span><span
      >recovery tuning</span
    ><span>dense kernels can apply</span>
    <strong>Distillation</strong><span>student architecture</span><span>student training</span><span
      >ordinary student runtime</span
    >
    <strong>Low-rank factorization</strong><span>W becomes AB</span><span
      >optional recovery tuning</span
    ><span>two smaller operators</span>
  </div>
</figure>
